{"tid":1670774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"陳同佳殺人後結果：由住公屋仔變成住住豪宅的上等人","createTime":"2019-10-23T06:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T16:12:40.000Z","uid":149978,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"734235c061bb774dff6a468bd286e47ed312374c","tid":1670774,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"今次真係：殺人放火金腰帶，修橋補路無屍骸<br />\n<br />\n在香港，只要你出左名，名氣衝出國際，影響力大。<br />\n那怕你係殺人犯，都一樣可以盡享榮華富貴。<br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n<strong>殺人後，入獄前被捕新聞</strong>：<br />\n現年20歲的<strong>陳同佳</strong>犯案前，在理工大學轄下香港專上學院修讀人力資源管理<strong>副學士課程</strong>，<strong>與父母及兄長居於九龍灣啟晴邨</strong>。據《東周刊》去年報道，陳同佳在兼職期間認識潘曉穎，2人自前年8月起正式拍拖，前者更自同年年底開始，屢次帶潘回家，2人不時在走廊「攬攬錫錫」。直至去年1月2人關係轉差，晚上回家時在走廊各靠一邊牆互不理睬。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>殺完人，出獄後：</strong><br />\n<br />\n台灣拖篋棄屍殺人案疑兇陳同佳，今早（23日）於壁屋懲教所刑滿出獄。聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴護送陳同佳離開後，於中環聖約翰座堂見傳媒指，<strong>陳同佳目前已離開京士柏山豪宅，</strong>料<em><strong>稍後與家人會面</strong></em>。管浩鳴稱，他們本來已購買機票到台灣，但台灣方面禁制他及陳同佳入境，因此已取消機票。陳同佳今日不會啟程到台灣，但具體的出發日期暫不未清楚。「佢做錯事係的確，但唔可以成為政治籌碼！」管浩鳴亦否認陳同佳被自首說法，目前需確保陳獲公平審訊，「佢只係一個細路仔嚟，希望大家畀機會佢改過自身。」中午有負責保護特首林鄭月娥的G4人員，一度於聖約翰座堂出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/%E3%80%90%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E8%97%8F%E5%B1%8D%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E7%84%A1%E6%A1%88%E5%BA%95%E6%9B%BE%E8%AE%80%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%89%AF%E5%AD%B8%E5%A3%AB-%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7%E8%AD%98%E6%BD%98%E6%9B%89%E7%A9%8E%E5%BE%8C%E7%86%B1%E6%88%80/ar-BBWoudm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Flocalnews%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25B1%258D%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25AE%2580%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E5%2585%25BC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%25BD%2598%25E6%259B%2589%25E7%25A9%258E%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%2588%2580%2Far-BBWoudm&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=1003afbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/%E3%80%90%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E8%97%8F%E5%B1%8D%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E7%84%A1%E6%A1%88%E5%BA%95%E6%9B%BE%E8%AE%80%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%89%AF%E5%AD%B8%E5%A3%AB-%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7%E8%AD%98%E6%BD%98%E6%9B%89%E7%A9%8E%E5%BE%8C%E7%86%B1%E6%88%80/ar-BBWoudm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/389352/%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E4%BA%AC%E5%A3%AB%E6%9F%8F%E5%B1%B1%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85-%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%95%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F389352%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584-%25E7%25A7%2598%25E5%25AF%2586%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259F%258F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2595%259F%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=7598db15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/389352/%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E4%BA%AC%E5%A3%AB%E6%9F%8F%E5%B1%B1%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85-%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%95%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3</a>"},{"pid":"de7e7c88a81a5df349cc13f600f8bb3c62733f5d","tid":1670774,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"【陳同佳出獄．直擊】陳同佳離開壁屋 鞠躬道歉後上車往九龍豪宅<br />\n<br />\n台灣拖篋棄屍殺人案疑兇陳同佳，被判監29個月，至今日（23日）刑滿出獄。至早上八時許，壁屋懲教所外有大批傳媒守候，車閘內有多名軍裝及便衣警員。至早上九時正，身穿藍色外套的陳同佳離開壁屋懲教所，他在聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴陪同下會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳表示，就事件會到台灣自首並指「我自己做了些無可挽救的錯事，為他們帶來好大的傷痛。」陳同佳希望女事主潘曉穎能夠安息，以及其能家人能釋懷。陳同佳鞠躬道歉後，與管浩鳴登上私家車離去，私家車向九龍區方向行駛，大批傳媒車輛尾隨。台灣拖篋棄屍殺人案疑兇陳同佳，被判監29個月，至今日（23日）刑滿出獄。至早上八時許，壁屋懲教所外有大批傳媒守候，車閘內有多名軍裝及便衣警員。至早上九時正，身穿藍色外套的陳同佳離開壁屋懲教所，他在聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴陪同下會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳表示，就事件會到台灣自首並指「我自己做了些無可挽救的錯事，為他們帶來好大的傷痛。」陳同佳希望女事主潘曉穎能夠安息，以及其能家人能釋懷。陳同佳鞠躬道歉後，與管浩鳴登上私家車離去，私家車向九龍區方向行駛，大批傳媒車輛尾隨。而<strong>陳同佳的車輛駛入私人屋苑京士柏山</strong>。至早上十時，管浩嗚與司機駛車離開，車上未見陳同佳。至早上十時，管浩嗚與司機駛車離開，車上未見陳同佳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/389209/%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%A3%81%E5%B1%8B-%E9%9E%A0%E8%BA%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%E5%BE%80%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F389209%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A3%2581%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E9%259E%25A0%25E8%25BA%25AC%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BE%2580%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=60cb357e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/389209/%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%A3%81%E5%B1%8B-%E9%9E%A0%E8%BA%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%E5%BE%80%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85</a>"},{"pid":"9ab7b1c70be4e0bf0dcde960f13c2fb27c2e73d6","tid":1670774,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"Pull<br />\nHk01帶風怪"},{"pid":"1bd32767021c35c37b6c4709b65622c57abd21c5","tid":1670774,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ab7b1c70be4e0bf0dcde960f13c2fb27c2e73d6","tid":1670774,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"Pull<br />\nHk01帶風怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"你上網搵其他新聞都差唔多"},{"pid":"90aef0c107f326c0f2648bfe45ee63d059d13da1","tid":1670774,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ab7b1c70be4e0bf0dcde960f13c2fb27c2e73d6","tid":1670774,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"Pull<br />\nHk01帶風怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20191023105148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20191023105148&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=5f6aab4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20191023105148</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳, 在香港洗黑錢案, 今天在壁屋監獄刑滿出獄, 他在監獄外發表簡單講話之後, 登上白色七人車離開, 受到大批傳媒車追訪, <strong>他的車之後進入了何文田屋苑京士柏山.</strong><br />\n        早上與接他出獄的香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴, 向傳媒表示, 陳同佳現時會暫時找個地方休息, 被問到陳同佳稍後會否回台灣自首, 管浩鳴無正面回應, 只是說希望先讓陳同佳沉澱一下."},{"pid":"db27675a00e4cfe37026c745f221302040676a0d","tid":1670774,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-10/23/37245.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-10%2F23%2F37245.html&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=b4cb4c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-10/23/37245.html</a>"},{"pid":"753346db39e5e5e48555487a6b2c2ece46a600a3","tid":1670774,"uid":164730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"京士柏山應該係中聯辦/管浩鳴嘅物業"},{"pid":"8f7383fcdc16b9b0059de6ede16b7eefc3da5bc4","tid":1670774,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"753346db39e5e5e48555487a6b2c2ece46a600a3","tid":1670774,"uid":164730,"like":4,"